                                            <div class="article-content">

                                                <h3 class="entry-title entry-title-small">
                                                    <a href="https://www.both.org/?p=10054" tabindex="0" rel="bookmark" title="The Linux Philosophy for SysAdmins, Tenet 19—Backup everything frequently">The Linux Philosophy for SysAdmins, Tenet 19—Backup everything frequently</a>
